        "locations": {
          "progression": 0,
          "position": 4,
          "totalProgression": 0.03571428571428571
        },
        "text": {
          "highlight": "So she was considering in her own mind (as well as she could, for the hot day made her feel very sleepy and stupid), whether the pleasure of making a daisy-chain would be worth the trouble of getting up and picking the daisies, when suddenly a White Rabbit with pink eyes ran close by her."
        }
      },
      "color": "red",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-23T11:46:03.130Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-23T11:46:03.130Z"
    },
